# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# CLIENT (PUBLIC) CONFIG
# EXPO_PUBLIC_* vars are embedded in the app bundle at build time, so they are
# PUBLIC. Only ever put publishable keys here. Row-Level Security protects the
# database, so the Supabase publishable (anon) key is safe to ship in clients.
#
# Server secrets — Resend API key, Cloudflare token, Expo access token, the
# Supabase service_role key — must NEVER live in this file or in any
# EXPO_PUBLIC_* variable. Keep them in Supabase Edge Function secrets
# (`supabase secrets set ...`) or your web host's environment settings.
# See docs/DEPLOYMENT.md.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

EXPO_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
EXPO_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=sb_publishable_xxxxxxxx
EXPO_PUBLIC_STRIPE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=pk_test_your-key-here
